orto:EarlyGrowthStage
        a       <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Class> , <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Resource>;
        <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf>
